title: [Cobblestone Path]
description: The sandy path leads up to the front of a large sandstone building surrounded by tall island grasses and small banana trees still too young to bear fruit.  Bright green shutters frame each window while a sturdy iron-banded door presents itself as the entrance.  A rusting iron stand surrounded by a ring of colorful island flowers rests along one side of the path adorned, with a tattered and faded stuffed parrot that sits upon it.

The sandy path leads up to the front of a large sandstone building surrounded by tall island grasses and small banana trees still too young to bear fruit.  Green shutters frame each window while a sturdy iron-banded door presents itself as the entrance.  An old iron stand with a ring of island flowers planted around it sits rusting along one side of the path, and a spluttering torch attached to the top of it illuminates the way.
